6. Security Properties
Property	Guaranteed by
Protocol fee (0.33%) always collected	Seaport (consideration item) + API validation
Listing MP fee (0.33%) always collected	Seaport (consideration item)
Buying MP fee (0.33%) always collected	Zone contract (validates tip)
Royalties paid when listing MP enforces	Seaport (consideration item)
Royalties optional when listing MP doesn't enforce	By design — no enforcement mechanism
Fees can't be modified after signing	EIP-712 signature (Seaport)
Buyer pays same amount everywhere	Fixed tip amount (0.33%) enforced by zone
Works if OOB API is down	Yes — zone is on-chain, Seaport is on-chain
Works with direct Seaport calls	Yes — zone validates all fulfillment paths
